Feedbacker
==========

Feedbacker provides a tab for users to contact developers from within the application


Installation
============
1. rake feedbacker:bootstrap

2. Add the following line to your application layout
<%= javascript_include_tag :feedbacker %>

3. Add the following line to your application layout before you call application.css. Override default settings in application.css
<%= stylesheet_link_tag :feedbacker %>

4. Add the following line right after the body tag in your application layout
<%= render(:partial => 'feedbacker/tab') unless current_user.is_guest? %>

5. Add to applicaton_controller.rb (may not be necessary after Rails 3.1)
helper :feedbacker

6. Add the folling like to confing/appliction.rb
config.active_record.observers = :remark_observer

5. Open config/initializers/feedbacker.rb and edit to taste


